{"tid":7596,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(逼害）一個月內兩次被罰上看台，摩連奴面臨兩場禁賽","createTime":"2016-11-28T01:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T03:42:31.000Z","uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5139a772d7547199a9629671bf1336b9dc4fe74b","tid":7596,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:53:46.000Z","msg":"《每日電訊報》消息，由於在不到一個月的時間內兩次被罰上看台，摩連奴將面臨禁賽兩場的處罰。<br />\n<br />\n在曼聯戰平韋斯咸的比賽中，普巴因為假摔而吃到一張黃牌。摩連奴對這個判罰極度不滿，於是憤怒地踢翻了水瓶，並且同球證進行理論。當值主裁隨即將他罰出場外。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_161128/20161128_474aa392b22a56578492wWGHUW9dnEmw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_161128%2F20161128_474aa392b22a56578492wWGHUW9dnEmw.jpg&h=21fb2c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於規則規定，被罰出球場的主教練無需參加賽後的新聞發佈會，因此助理教練法里亞代替摩連奴接受了媒體的採訪。法里亞透露，雖然普巴插水, 但對普巴出示黃牌的決定仍然讓摩連奴出離憤怒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/acdaacca5f084f8fac972c90e519df99/tumblr_ohbdn1df9L1tf8a5ao1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Facdaacca5f084f8fac972c90e519df99%2Ftumblr_ohbdn1df9L1tf8a5ao1_500.gif&h=185da115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這張黃牌將會使普巴錯過週中主場對陣鐵錘幫的聯賽盃。<br />\n<br />\n上個月對陣般尼的比賽，由於中場時在球員通道內口頭指責當值主裁克拉滕伯格，摩連奴曾被禁賽一場，並罰款8000歐元。<br />\n<br />\n此番被禁賽，摩連奴可能同樣會面臨本賽季的第三次罰款，另外一次是因為在對陣利物浦之前發表了不當言論。"},{"pid":"9ae3de5bdd93e87677e57c5605a7993e89a58403","tid":7596,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:55:09.000Z","msg":"英超賽會知唔知咩叫魔性"},{"pid":"0387a02543786d08a41786ee8d04f59f53c56916","tid":7596,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"普包幾勁"},{"pid":"2a24c0d35004021ffd629673da475439013a96ef","tid":7596,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:11:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc34441b182cd59c7fd15738263b4f7fa6d1ebb3","tid":7596,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"魔性"},{"pid":"68448f9e20a59d2680ea406df9d44ad3af1d4bed","tid":7596,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:16:11.000Z","msg":"魔性回歸"},{"pid":"0bc33bbb70a4dd8c624d72320de1282119061b22","tid":7596,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"雖然普巴插水, 但對普巴出示黃牌的決定仍然讓摩連奴憤怒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ab31368def4900840b83c01f315704d870ed6c","tid":7596,"uid":1017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:18:20.000Z","msg":"踢下水樽都趕，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d1fb9a7154569f3918b1203ccc66bfa00dc533","tid":7596,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"摩佬：球證和英超主帥參與「反曼聯運動」。"},{"pid":"878ec3d5650eefce0aa1ae28c825ae45455ea00c","tid":7596,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"成日逼害我daddy 足總死全家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c832351967e33a8885a9a3f4b21fcbae2d9a0cd","tid":7596,"uid":15950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ef6096a4cedfaf7919e3967150cac59dae9662","tid":7596,"uid":2927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"反摩會戰勝歸來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88a5b866f50f77c7e04b2b615855aa3d429e873","tid":7596,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踢下水樽都趕